name: Sour Diesel
notes: Slow driving ride, none of the enjoyable perks along the way, gets the job done, budget friendly

name: GMO
taste: Garlic, hints of pepper and onions
Expansion: Smooth inhale, slight chest bump on them big hits, pleasant after taste
notes: Fast Ride with some nice features, very enjoyable

name: Mount Hood Magic
notes: Nice ride but short lived, hash after, can get alot better if left in the jar awhile

name: MoonBow #112
taste: citrusy berry delight (Trix or Fruity pebbles)
smell: Sweet berrys hints of pepper garlic, pine & nuts oh my!!
Expansion: Smooth inhale, nice cozy chest hug
notes: All the perks are in this ride, Awesome Job Archive!!! I hope you keep this one in your line up

name: Animal Sherbmints x Purple Wreck
taste: Light lemony citrus, hints of pepper garlic sweet earthy
smell: Sweet shreaded carrots, hints of that lemony citrus
Expansion: Smooth inhale, very light chest bump on them big hits
notes: Nice ride, budget friendly for the features.

name: Planet Marshmallow
taste: inhale: bitter, sour apple, almost chemical / exhale pure magic: citrusy berry apple delight (Trix or Fruity pebbles)
smell: Sour apple, grape berry mix jolly rancher
notes: This ride was pleasantly surprising, first the taste buds say spit it out then they say give me more! budget friendly.
